data.text:
Cocke County, TNGenWeb

Queries October 1998 to January 1999

These queries are provided as a research aid for the information they may contain. Please be aware that due to the age of these postings contact information may no longer be current. To avoid spammers, email is linked to from the submitter's name below their message. If you have posted any queries on these pages we would be happy to update your email address.

PJ Summers, Co-host Cocke County TNGenWeb.
